<strong>About This Extension</strong>

Simple extension that helps to quickly open file or project folder with <a href="http://macromates.com/">TextMate</a> with <a href="http://alfredapp.com/">Alfred</a>. Can be used with Alfred navigation as action. Mind that extensions works only with Alfred <a href="http://www.alfredapp.com/powerpack">Powerpack</a>.

This extension can be updated via <a href="http://jdfwarrior.tumblr.com/updater">Extension Updater for Alfred</a>.

<strong>How To Use This Extension</strong>

Use #1: textmate &lt;input file name or path&gt;
Example: textmate /Sites/example.com/ - open project from "/Sites/example.com/" folder
Example: textmate ~/Documents/notes.txt

Use #2: Type file or folder name and choose action "Open with Textmate"
Example: notes.txt =&gt; Open with Textmate

